Name: UCSB
Descriptions: A very beautiful university located in Santa Barbara

Name: Eureka!
Descriptions: A very tasty American fast food restaurant with a very good spicy fried chicken burger

Name: Santa barbara Airport
Descriptions: A small airport in Santa Barbara where people can choose to make short trips

Name: Target
Descriptions: Students and local residents enjoy shopping for household goods at this supermarket. For students living in the school dormitory, it is easy to go to the supermarket for shopping.

Name: stearns wharf
Descriptions: It is a marina with many seafood spots as well as seafood restaurants nearby. You can also enjoy a very beautiful sea view

Name: South Coast Railroad Museum
Descriptions: This is such a fun little train museum, that also features a small scale train that you can buy a ticket ($2.50) to ride around the grounds. Great for train lovers, history buffs, kids, or the kids at heart.
